        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Look not behind thee — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "He must not loiter by the way; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "stay not in all the plain — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "For it would all be made one dead sea; he must not take up short of the place of refuge appointed him; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "escape to the mountain — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Such are the commands given to those who, through grace, are delivered out of a sinful state. 1st, Return not to sin and Satan, for that is ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "looking back to Sodom. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "2d, Rest not in the world, for that is ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "staying in the plain.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "3d, Reach toward Christ and heaven, for that is ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "escaping to the mountain, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "short of which we must not take up.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
